linux window

# permission
sudo su root


# cd to folder C
cd /mnt/c


# get all folders and files from url
wget -r -np -nH --cut-dirs=3 -R index.html http://hostname/aaa/bbb/ccc/ddd/
Explanation:

It will download all files and subfolders in ddd directory
-r : recursively
-np : not going to upper directories, like ccc/â€¦
-nH : not saving files to hostname folder
--cut-dirs=3 : but saving it to ddd by omitting first 3 folders aaa, bbb, ccc
-R index.html : excluding index.html files

#build scss to css
sass --no-source-map --watch scss:css


